00:19:10.960 --> 00:19:13.168
we'll talk about graphs here
in a couple weeks-- over

00:19:13.168 --> 00:19:14.519
and over again, people do this.

00:19:14.519 --> 00:19:16.560
They draw it, it looks
like this, you accept that

00:19:16.560 --> 00:19:17.620
and then you're dead.

00:19:17.620 --> 00:19:20.190
Everything else,
there's no hope.

00:19:20.190 --> 00:19:23.080
Everybody clear what went
wrong in this picture?

00:19:23.080 --> 00:19:25.630
How we got off track?

00:19:25.630 --> 00:19:29.100
This is sort of a nasty one.

00:19:29.100 --> 00:19:29.600
OK.

00:19:32.120 --> 00:19:34.586
Now one of the nice
