00:19:36.710 --> 00:19:38.775
out step by step,
and there's a bug,

00:19:38.775 --> 00:19:40.620
you can go back and find it.

00:19:40.620 --> 00:19:42.240
And so this, I
didn't sort of really

00:19:42.240 --> 00:19:43.770
write it out very
well step by step,

00:19:43.770 --> 00:19:46.740
and it was harder to find.

00:19:46.740 --> 00:19:49.190
Now, all right, so we
