01:18:28.430 --> 01:18:31.750
it becomes easier to
prove, even a harder thing.

01:18:31.750 --> 01:18:33.960
And so a general
rule with induction

01:18:33.960 --> 01:18:36.505
is if you don't first
succeed, try, try again.

01:18:36.505 --> 01:18:39.130
Well, the rule with induction is
